                <th>Jami narxi</th>
                <th>Oyiga</th>
                <th>1 oylik bilan farq (oyiga)</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
              <tr><td>1 oy</td><td>57 000 so'm</td><td>57 000 so'm</td><td>—</td></tr>
              <tr><td>3 oy</td><td>172 000 so'm</td><td>~57 333 so'm</td><td>+0.6% (qimmatroq)</td></tr>
              <tr><td>6 oy</td><td>232 000 so'm</td><td>~38 667 so'm</td><td>−32% (arzonroq)</td></tr>
              <tr><td>12 oy</td><td>422 000 so'm</td><td>~35 167 so'm</td><td>−38% (arzonroq)</td></tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>

          <p>Birinchi qiziqarli kuzatuv: <strong>3 oylik paket 1 oylikdan oyiga arzonroq emas</strong>. 172 000 ÷ 3 = 57 333 — bu 1 oylik narxidan (57 000) bir oz qimmat. Demak, 3 oylik tejam mantig'i yo'q. 6 oylik va 12 oylik paketlar haqiqiy tejam beradi.</p>

          <h2>Birlik narxi — qaysi paket eng tejamkor?</h2>

          <p>Aniq tejam tahlili. 1 yilda Premium foydalansangiz har bir variant qancha turadi:</p>

          <table class="price-table">
